data.about: Focuses and passionate on programming-tech education, software development, software requirements analysis, and software business strategy. Bagas also proficient in programming languages such as Javascript & Typescript along with several frameworks and libraries such as Next Js, React Js, React Native or task management on Jira/Trello. He was handling backend services configuration such as Firebase, while also handling state management and manipulation using third-party libraries like Redux, Universally Unique Identifier (UUID), also middleware such as Redux-Thunk/Saga. He was able to using Express JS to work on API development as well as query management with MySQL. Ever released a mobile application on the Play Store and App Store platforms called IJSL - Indonesian Junior Soccer League .
